@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ithhno(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v0 + 0.07 + tmp + 0.31)))
    tmp = ((0.99 + wp.abs(v1 + 0.21)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.94) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.37)))
    v2 = ((0.14 + (tmp + 0.57 * v2 + 0.15)) / wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.22)))
    data[tid] = v0
